data.description: Welcome to a retreat nestled in the serene embrace of nature, designed for leisure and entertainment. As you approach the residence, its lush landscaping will captivate you. Inside, discover a home with 6 bedrooms and 4.2 baths. The main level greets you with two spacious bedrooms, strategically placed for convenience and privacy. The primary bedroom on this level features double French doors leading to a fully screened porch. Ascend to the upper level to find two or three additional bedrooms, each offering ample space and stunning views of the landscape. The larger bedroom can also be a wonderful media room with half bath. In the basement, a haven for entertainment and relaxation awaits. The finished terrace level is a design masterpiece, featuring a stylish full kitchen and plenty of seating, ideal for unwinding. On cool evenings, cozy up by the fireplace, enjoying the warmth and ambiance as you reflect on the day's events. This inviting space is perfect for hosting gatherings or relaxing after a day of golf, providing a beautiful setting for making memories. Outside, the property's vast grounds present infinite possibilities for recreation and relaxation. Stroll along the lake's tranquil shores, play a round on the nearby championship golf course, enjoy pickleball, bocce, tennis, or swim in the pool, all while taking in the scenic views. This property offers a seamless blend of comfort and recreational amenities, ensuring a lifestyle of exceptional luxury. Experience the ultimate in lakeside living and championship golf at this remarkable retreat. Priced below appraisal
